Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.35,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}あの日からずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:31.61,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,500)}泣かないと決めてきたけどq
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:37.16,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}痛みを重ねても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:42.29,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}何かを許せずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:45.71,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}もう戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.21,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}いくつもの日々
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:53.30,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僕はまだ何もできずに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:58.55,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}君のいた記憶の破片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:04.43,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1500)}またひとつ 消えてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.44,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今日よりもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.19,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:15.32,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この声がいつか届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.70,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歩き続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.41,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風が止んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:25.12,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}君を探して空見上げるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:32.46,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}夜明けの先に光が射すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:38.01,ED5JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}虹がかかるよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------ED5CN------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.35,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:31.61,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,500)}我下定决心不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:37.16,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}即使伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:42.29,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}有些东西也从不退让
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:45.71,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一去不返的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.21,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:53.30,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我依然无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:58.55,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}曾经有你的点滴记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:04.43,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1500)}又有一段  即将消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.44,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想比今日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.19,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:15.32,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}强到有一天能够传达这心声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.70,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.41,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}待到风停时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:25.12,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}我会仰望天空寻觅你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:32.46,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}拂晓前方光芒照耀大地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:38.01,ED5CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,1000)}虹彩跨越天际
