Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:32.75,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(400,400)}此刻那雪白的景色正在召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:39.26,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)}我将前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:48.22,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}走在迷茫的旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.02,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,0)}灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:57.11,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}一日一换的地图  浸透了多少个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:59.48,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:03.53,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}即便如我这般窄小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:09.62,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}是否也终能到达那片云之彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:11.25,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.79,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几度受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:15.88,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}仿佛洗刷了心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:17.42,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:19.59,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}点点雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:22.80,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重复进行着漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.68,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}笔直的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:28.39,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}纵横交错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:31.98,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}也不知将去向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:33.27,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向着远方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:34.85,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:40.69,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}淡淡的残像  铭刻在眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:42.61,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:46.45,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,500)}无论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:48.74,OP2CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,0)}都一定能传到
